flown from one military prison to another he had heard about other 
prisoners thrown out of helicopters alive martinezbaca said 
another time when he was led away for interrogation and torture 
his jailers told him to say his last words and acted as if he would 
be killed he said 
the military finally allowed him to leave the country in 1980 
just as argentinas supreme court was about to order his release 
