organizations executive director said tuesday termination doesnt 
become final until approved by the groups board of directors 
which meets next february 
if they cant show the code and the logo like the good 
housekeeping seal of approval on their programs it should affect 
their donations said the rev benjamin l armstrong executive 
director of the 1400member organization 
